---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Section, SectionContent, SectionProse } from "@/components/ui/section";
import { site } from "@/config";
---

<Layout>
  <Section size="sm">
    <SectionContent class="items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">{site.name}</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        {site.role}
        <br />
        {site.location}
      </p>
    </SectionContent>
    <SectionProse class="mx-auto">
      <p>
        I love building from zero; where everything needs to be done.
        Prototyping, creating, sharing, discovering. That's what drives me every
        day. I fail, I break things, I start over. Each time a little bigger
        than the last.
      </p>
      <p>
        My weeks are eclectic. I might be painting a theater set on Monday,
        shipping features in an app on Wednesday, and tinkering with hardware on
        Thursday. I just like it when no two days look the same.
      </p>
      <p>
        To move forward you need to be organized, plan, and then do. Do, do, do.
        That's the most important thing; take action. Don't wait for the right
        moment. Don't plan forever. Don't overthink. Just go. Action creates
        results. Results create joy. And you keep going.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's where my drive comes from; the joy of creating, seeing what I
        build being used, being useful, bringing something to others and to
        myself. That's how I live, day by day.
      </p>
      <p>
        It feels like I'm writing these words for myself; because they are
        things I keep telling myself.
      </p>
    </SectionProse>
  </Section>
</Layout>
